name: .QF File Extension
summary: Learn about .QF files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Web page template created with Qompose (pronounced "compose"), an HTML templating language; allows multiple pages to be built from the same basic layout; uses "tokens" to specify different sections of each page.

content: Published Qompose Web pages also end in ".qf" (rather than ".html"). They are processed by the Qompose CGI script installed on the Web server.
